SUMMARY:Part Closure: WINDRUSH LINE: Saturday 14 and Sunday 15 June\, no 
 service between Surrey Quays and Crystal Palace / West Croydon. There will
  also be no SOUTHERN services between London Bridge and Crystal Palace / 
 East Croydon (via Forest Hill). For New Cross Gate\, use New Cross\, and 
 local buses for Penge West\, Anerley and Norwood Junction. Replacement 
 buses operate between New Cross Gate and Crystal Palace via Brockley\, 
 Honor Oak Park\, Forest Hill and Sydenham.
